headline.print_headline: Flyhalf Cooper Re-Signs With Australian Rugby Through 2015
headline.main: Flyhalf Cooper Re-Signs With Australian Rugby Through 2015

lead_paragraph: Flyhalf Quade Cooper has made himself available for World Cup selection after signing a contract extension with the Australian Rugby Union until the end of 2015.
